---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="The Programme – DGIS Fortaleza 2026" lang="en">
<div class="sec-dark" style="padding:52px 24px 48px;">
  <div class="container" style="padding:0;">
    <span class="eyebrow-white">The Programme</span>
    <h1 class="page-h1-white" style="margin-top:10px;">Real surgical immersion on live patients</h1>
    <div class="gold-bar"></div>
    <p class="lead-white" style="max-width:600px;">In Fortaleza every surgery is performed by the students themselves. Direct clinical practice with expert supervision and digital guided planning.</p>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="sec-white">
  <div class="section">
    <div class="grid-2" style="gap:48px;align-items:start;margin-bottom:64px;">
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:36px;">
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Clinical approach</span>
          <h2 class="sec-h2" style="margin-top:10px;">You are the lead surgeon</h2>
          <div class="sky-bar"></div>
          <p class="lead" style="margin-bottom:14px;">Unlike other training programmes, in DGIS Fortaleza students do not attend as observers: they <strong>operate</strong>. Each student acts as lead surgeon in every surgical session, with direct supervision from the teaching team.</p>
          <p class="lead">The programme covers three digital guided surgery protocols, from most to least complex, with postoperative verification sessions (planned vs. executed) at the end of each day.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <span class="eyebrow">Methodology</span>
          <h2 class="sec-h2" style="margin-top:10px;">Complete digital workflow</h2>
          <div class="sky-bar"></div>
          <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;">
            {[
              'Digital planning of each case before surgery',
              'Peer review and validation with the teaching team',
              'Execution of surgery as lead surgeon',
              'Postoperative planned vs. executed verification',
              'Precision analysis and clinical feedback',
            ].map(i => (
              <li style="display:flex;gap:10px;font-size:.88rem;color:var(--sl700);word-wrap:break-word;">
                <svg width="16" height="16" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:3px;" fill="none" stroke="var(--sky500)" stroke-width="2.5" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>{i}
              </li>
            ))}
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;">
        <div class="img-frame"><img src="/pptx_images/image8.jpeg" alt="Team surgery" style="height:220px;width:100%;object-fit:cover;" /><div class="img-cap">Hands-on surgery with real patient</div></div>
        <div class="img-frame"><img src="/pptx_images/image4.jpeg" alt="Surgeon with loupe" style="height:180px;width:100%;object-fit:cover;" /><div class="img-cap">Optical magnification in guided surgery</div></div>
        <div class="img-frame"><img src="/pptx_images/image5.jpeg" alt="Live streaming" style="height:160px;width:100%;object-fit:cover;" /><div class="img-cap">Live surgical broadcast</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="center mx-auto" style="margin-bottom:36px;">
      <span class="eyebrow">Every day</span>
      <h2 class="sec-h2" style="margin-top:10px;">Daily Digital Guided Surgery flow</h2>
      <div class="sky-bar"></div>
      <p class="lead">A typical programme day: clear structure with maximum clinical value.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid-4" style="margin-bottom:56px;">
      {[
        {n:'01', icon:'🖥️', t:'Digital planning', d:'Review and design of the surgical plan using digital guide software for each clinical case of the day.'},
        {n:'02', icon:'👁️', t:'Peer review',      d:'Validation of the plan with the teaching team before the surgical intervention.'},
        {n:'03', icon:'🦷', t:'Surgery sessions', d:'4 rounds of guided surgery per day. The student operates as lead surgeon in each session.'},
        {n:'04', icon:'📊', t:'Post-op check',    d:'Planned vs. executed analysis to measure precision at the end of each working day.'},
      ].map(s => (
        <div class="card" style="text-align:center;">
          <div class="card-accent"></div>
          <div class="card-body">
            <div style="width:40px;height:40px;background:var(--sky800);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 12px;color:#fff;font-weight:900;font-size:.8rem;">{s.n}</div>
            <div style="font-size:1.7rem;margin-bottom:10px;">{s.icon}</div>
            <h4 style="font-weight:800;font-size:.88rem;color:var(--sky900);margin-bottom:8px;">{s.t}</h4>
            <p style="font-size:.79rem;color:var(--sl500);line-height:1.65;word-wrap:break-word;">{s.d}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
    <div class="cta-banner">
      <div>
        <h3 style="font-weight:800;font-size:1.1rem;color:var(--sky900);margin-bottom:6px;">In Fortaleza you are the surgeon</h3>
        <p style="font-size:.85rem;color:var(--sl500);">100% surgeries by students · Continuous expert supervision · Accredited diploma</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/en/registration" class="btn btn-sky btn-lg">Apply now →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</Layout>
